Rating: 4
Very easy, very yummy. We get two tenderloins and make extra medallions because, leftovers. I find the sauce overwhelming to the meat (much as I love yogurt and mayo and capers) and we often stick to lemon wedges instead. The only thing I change in this recipe is to use a metal grid in the baking pan so the medallions aren't resting on the metal and getting mooshy on the bottom. Highly recommended.

