Rating: 4
Delicious, Milanese-style preparation of pork tenderloin medallions. Just the right amount of frying and baking resulting in a juicy, springy pink center, a resilient, crisp coating and lots of flavor. The caper-yogurt sauce perfectly compliments together with a nice cool glass of Slovenian Jeruzalem White Sauvignon.

